罗阿讷市区内共有一个派出所<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/roanne-42300|title=COMMISSARIAT DE POLICE À ROANNE 42300|accessdate=2019-09-19|author=demarchesadministratives.fr|language=fr|publisher=demarchesadministratives.fr|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503101534/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/roanne-42300|dead-url=no}}</ref>、一个消防队和一个国家宪兵队<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/roanne-42300|title=GENDARMERIE À ROANNE 42300|accessdate=2019-09-19|author=demarchesadministratives.fr|language=fr|publisher=demarchesadministratives.fr|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503103209/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/roanne-42300|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

